Smart Choice Communications, also known as SCC, is an Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS) company that acts as a single source solution for businesses. Their services include, but are not limited to: voice, internet, data, analytics, collaboration, monitoring, network security, design, installation and support. Smart Choice Communications is based out of New York City and have network operations in Missouri.  Smart Choice Communications has helped hundreds of thousands of enterprise users to grow and maintain their businesses.
